OL,4,CDeal with tax avoidance in Budget - MP
OL,5, The government should use next week's
OL,6, Budget to crack down on issues of tax
OL,7, avoidance raised by the release of the
OL,8, Paradise Papers, an ex-minister says.
OL,10,FLabour MP Dame Margaret Hodge, who led
OL,11,Fan emergency debate on the leaked
OL,12,Fdocuments, said tax avoidance was "a
OL,13,Fnational and international disgrace".
OL,15,FShe called for new laws to force big
OL,16,Ffirms to report profits more openly.
OL,18,FTreasury Minister Mel Stride said the
OL,19,Fgovernment had a "very strong track
OL,20,Frecord" in tackling tax avoidance.
